	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002164_0001"/><!--pb/@n='35r'-->
<!--MH: headed notepaper-->
<lb/><p rend="right">20<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> Jan /1865 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I send you by today<reg>'</reg>s 
<lb/>Book Post 550-669 
<lb/>pages Manuscript 
<lb/>and I shall now 
<lb/>get to revision as 
<lb/>quickly as I can - 
<lb/>I have still a 
<lb/>journey to <placeName>Lake 
<lb/>Nyassa</placeName> alone to 
<lb/>write &amp; a note 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002164_0002"/><!--pb/@n='35v'-->
<lb/>about the voyage 
<lb/>to <placeName>Bombay</placeName> and 
<lb/>will lose no time 
<lb/>I ought to have been 
<lb/>off ere now - though 
<lb/>I have every 
<w>com-<lb break="no"/>fort</w> that I can 
<lb/>desire here I often 
<lb/>take a sore longing 
<lb/>to be in <placeName>Africa</placeName><reg>.</reg>
<lb/>My family is 
<lb/>my only chain<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I <choice><sic>recieved</sic><corr>received</corr></choice> the 
<lb/>plates &amp; will 
<lb/>attend to your 
<lb/>suggestion<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002164_0003"/><!--pb/@n='36r'-->
<lb/>I was informed 
<lb/>by <persName>M<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi><add place="above">Young</add></persName> of the Â£44 17 
<lb/>but did not think 
<lb/>of acknowledging 
<lb/>it myself - that 
<lb/>is the channel 
<lb/>I wish anything 
<lb/>you may have 
<lb/>to give me to 
<lb/>go through and 
<lb/>am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002164_0004"/><!--pb/@n='36v'-->
<lb/>The artist seems to have 
<lb/>succeeded very well 
<lb/>but I should like the 
<lb/>Baobab more like 
<lb/>the Photo - as it is 
<lb/>mentioned in <persName>Com. 
<lb/>Owen's</persName> book as 60 feet 
<lb/>in circumference - the 
<lb/>Fig tree in the middle &amp; 
<lb/>Bombax trees behind 
<lb/>the house are very 
<lb/>characteristic in their 
<lb/>shapes &amp; I have put 
<lb/>a note in pencil 
<lb/>on the enclosed drawing 
<lb/>to that effect<reg>.</reg></p>
			
